2. MANDATORY TOKEN AUTHORIZATION
Access to, and execution of, the protected RTL logic (including encrypted .v.enc files) 
is strictly managed via the TokenClaw-DR gateway. No party is permitted to:
   a. Bypass the remote authentication handshake.
   b. Use the logic for commercial tape-out or manufacturing without a valid, 
      architect-issued Token.
   c. Reverse-engineer the encrypted physical layer assets.

